| "turn right" voice command        | Robot turns right                                        | Responds & turns right                             | Pass      |
| "spin around" voice command       | Robot spins in place                                     | Responds & spins around                            | Pass      |
| "stop" voice command              | Robot stops movement                                     | Responds & stops immediately                       | Pass      |
| "walk around" voice command       | Robot explores freely, avoids obstacles & cliffs          | Moves autonomously, avoids obstacles & cliffs       | Pass      |
| Obstacle detection at 5cm         | Stops before collision                                   | Stops at ~4-6cm                                    | Pass      |
| Cliff detection (table edge)      | Halts immediately                                        | Halts within 1cm of edge                           | Pass      |
| "environment report" command      | Reports temperature and humidity                         | Displays temp/humidity on screen                   | Pass      |
